-f[{a,b,c} Comma-separated field names to include or exclude, e.g. a,b,c.]
-o[Retain fields in the order specified by -f rather than in]
-x[Exclude, rather than include, the field names specified by -f.]
--complement[Exclude, rather than include, the field names specified by -f.]
-r[Treat field names as regular expressions. "ab", "a.*b" will]
-h
--help
